# 🏥 Healthcare Readmission Analysis

This project analyzes hospital discharge data to study readmission patterns using Python and visualizes insights using Power BI.

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Python (Google Colab)
- Power BI

## 📊 Key Steps
- Cleaned raw dataset (missing values, formatting)
- Generated KPIs and dashboards in Power BI
- Visualized readmission trends by age, gender, diagnosis

## 📁 Files
- `healthcare_cleaning.ipynb`: Python notebook for data cleaning
- `readmission_dashboard.png`: Screenshot of Power BI dashboard
